headline.main: Space and Missiles; A Giant Step Toward the Moon

results.snippet: Flying men to the moon, only a dream for centuries, ranks as the foremost engineering challenge of our time and a distinct possibility in this decade.
results.lead_paragraph: Flying men to the moon, only a dream for centuries, ranks as the foremost engineering challenge of our time and a distinct possibility in this decade.

results.abstract: Jane's All the World's Aircraft (pub), holding war between US and USSR unthinkable, suggests 2 nations enter 'mutual survival pact' against nuclear potential of Communist China and France
results.snippet: LONDON, Nov. 28 (UPI)-- An authoritative publication on military power said today that the United States and the Soviet Union should enter a "mutual survival pact" against the nuclear potential of Communist China and France.
results.lead_paragraph: LONDON, Nov. 28 (UPI)-- An authoritative publication on military power said today that the United States and the Soviet Union should enter a "mutual survival pact" against the nuclear potential of Communist China and France.
